						<div class="postbody">X position, I don't know. I was scrolling the screen with a half cut-off sprite where the rendering was disabled, and the sprite seems to be able to display itself on all parts of the scanline, so it might be disabled in hblank.
<br />
<br />Y position, I'm not good at counting blank scanlines, but it's definitely 16 or more scanlines before the natural end of the frame. Looks like maybe 24.</div>

