				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p106129">Re: PowerPak + Tetramino = sprite flicker</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=106129#p106129"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sun Jan 13, 2013 5:15 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
